title: EXTRAORDINARY - Best Motivational Speeches Compilation - MORNING MOTIVATION
itunes:title: EXTRAORDINARY - Best Motivational Speeches Compilation - MORNING MOTIVATION
itunes:subtitle: Motiversity
description:
Overcome the notion that you must be regular. It robs you of the chance to be EXTRAORDINARY! One of the BEST MORNING MOTIVATIONAL SPEECHES!!

"The difference between ordinary and extraordinary is a little extra." Featuring Coach Pain (https://bit.ly/CoachPainMotiversity), Marcus Taylor (https://bit.ly/MarcusTaylorMotiversity), Brian Bullock (https://bit.ly/BrianBullockMotiversity), Jessica Houston (https://bit.ly/DrJessicaHoustonMotiversity), Nathan Harmon (https://bit.ly/NathanHarmonMotiversity), Walter Bond (https://bit.ly/WalterBondMotiversity) and Ronald A. Burgess Jr. (https://bit.ly/RonaldABurgessJrMotiversity).


Music by Secession Studios (https://bit.ly/SecessionStudiosYouTube), Really Slow Motion (https://bit.ly/RSMMusic), Audiojungle (https://audiojungle.net/), and Whitesand (https://www.youtube.com/c/WhitesandComposer).



Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
